babyDoll.name: Sweetie Pie
babyDoll.description: Sweetie Pie is an adorable baby doll with a soft body and lifelike features. She comes with a cute outfit and a pacifier.

babyDoll.name: Cuddly Cutie
babyDoll.description: Cuddly Cutie is a huggable baby doll with realistic eyes and movable arms and legs. She comes with a diaper and a bottle.

babyDoll.name: Tiny Treasures
babyDoll.description: Tiny Treasures is a small-sized baby doll with a soft body and a beautiful dress. She comes with a matching headband.

barbieDolls.name: Fashionista Barbie
barbieDolls.description: Fashionista Barbie is a stylish doll with a wide range of trendy outfits and accessories. She comes with multiple fashion pieces for mix-and-match fun.

barbieDolls.name: Dreamhouse Barbie
barbieDolls.description: Dreamhouse Barbie is a glamorous doll that comes with her own dream house. The house features multiple rooms and interactive accessories for imaginative play.

barbieDolls.name: Princess Barbie
barbieDolls.description: Princess Barbie is a regal doll dressed in a beautiful princess gown. She comes with a tiara and a magical wand for enchanting adventures.

latiYellowDolls.name: Sunny Sprite
latiYellowDolls.description: Sunny Sprite is a charming Lati Yellow doll with a bright personality. She has a sunny yellow outfit and a whimsical hat.

latiYellowDolls.name: Rosy Blossom
latiYellowDolls.description: Rosy Blossom is a delightful Lati Yellow doll with a blooming personality. She wears a lovely floral dress and carries a bouquet of flowers.

latiYellowDolls.name: Misty Moonbeam
latiYellowDolls.description: Misty Moonbeam is an enchanting Lati Yellow doll with a dreamy personality. She wears a shimmering moon-themed outfit and carries a magical wand.
